info.installInstructions:
üö® IMPORTANT! DO THIS BEFORE INSTALLING!
üåÄ Inside Vortex, open Settings on the left bar and navigate to the Mods tab.
‚õî At the bottom of the Mods tab, disable "use recommentations from the mod manifests".
‚òù Not doing this will prevent proper installation.

**Experiencing an issue with Vortex?**
The most common issue is that a mod did not install correctly. This issue can be solved by filtering "Enabled" mods inside Vortex, selecting them all, and then clicking Reinstall in the bottom menu (do not right-click!)
¬†
Other common issues occur because:
- Mods are installed more than once (please delete all mods in folder and reinstall from collection)
- Mods from another pack have not been uninstalled properly
¬†
You can find [Vortex Support on Discord here](http://discord.gg/nexusmods). Office hours are 9-5 GMT Mon-Thurs.
You can find the [Vortex Support Wiki here](http://wiki.nexusmods.com/index.php/Category:Vortex) and their [Stardew Setup Guide here.](https://wiki.nexusmods.com/index.php/Modding_Stardew_Valley_with_Vortex)
¬†
**Experiencing an issue with the Stardew Valley VERY Expanded Collection?**
The game client will lag and possibly crash when loading or creating a new character. Please be patient and do not use your keyboard or mouse until the game has fully loaded.

If you experience further issues, you can share a link to your [SMAPI log using this website](https://smapi.io/log) on the forum for this collection.
¬†
Still need assistance? Consider joining [my streamer Discord server](http://discord.gg/de2NrHXuty) and hopping in the Stardew Valley channel!
¬†
I am not Nexus or Vortex staff.
